root: ^Dylan: "Here it is! I'm so glad it's still here."
^Dylan: "...Thinking back on it now, I really wish I spoke up about the slip."
^Dylan: "Mom and dad were always busy, but they tried as they could to make time for me. I should've trusted they would listen."
^Dylan: "Maybe if I go and ask properly this time, I can fix things."
^Casper: 'Atta boy. Humans can't read minds like cats can.'
^Casper: 'Communicating helps to ensure everyone's needs are heard.'
